These are Puzzles for 4x4 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-1::.
The people have 4 different hobbies: sudoku, magic-tricks, cooking, drawing
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, electrician, nurse, architect
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: pop, classical, reggae, metal
4 different pets are kept: horse, rat, goat, pony
1. the electrician is the person who's hobby is sudoku##1
2. the fan of metal is on the left of the owner of the rat##1
3. the fan of reggae is the lawyer##1
4. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the right of the electrician##1
5. the nurse is on the right of the person who's hobby is magic-tricks##1
6. the fan of pop is on the left of the fan of classical##1
7. the electrician is the owner of the horse##1
8. the fan of classical is on the right of the owner of the goat##1
9. the person who's hobby is drawing is on the left of the owner of the goat##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2     |    3    |     4      |
| Hobby         | sudoku  | drawing  | magic-tricks | cooking |
| Job           | electrician | lawyer | architect  | nurse  |
| Music-Genre   | metal       | reggae      | pop | classical      |
| Pet           | horse          | rat     | goat    | pony     |

