.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-2::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: milk, coffee, water, fanta
There 4 different types of food: radish, pumpkin, peach, peas
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: metal, house, techno, d&b
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: sailing, skateboarding, parkour, rugby
1. the person eating radish is on the far right##1
2. the fan of d&b is the person who's sport is sailing##1
3. the person eating peach is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
4. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person eating pumpkin##1
5. the fan of d&b is on the left of the fan of metal##1
6. the person drinking water is the fan of techno##1
7. the fan of house is on the left of the person drinking coffee##1
8. the person who's sport is parkour is on the left of the person drinking milk##1
9. the person who's sport is sailing is on the right of the person who's sport is rugby##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage      | water     | milk       | coffee | fanta        |
| Food          | peas     | pumpkin       | peach   | radish   |
| Music-Genre   | techno      | house       | d&b     | metal    |
| Sport         | parkour | rugby | sailing | skateboarding |

