.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-3::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: soy-milk, almond-milk, fanta, iced-tea
The people have 4 different jobs:  writer, dressmaker, firefighter, photographer
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: mystery, spy, epic, zombie
4 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, frog, fish
 1. the person drinking iced-tea is the owner of the fish##1
 2. the person drinking fanta is on the far right##1
 3. the person watching epic movies is on the far right##1
 4. the owner of the frog is on the left of the owner of the cat##1
 5. the person drinking soy-milk is on the right of the person watching mystery movies##1
 6. the person watching mystery movies is on the left of the person watching spy movies##1
 7. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the dressmaker##1
 8. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the writer##1
 9. the person drinking soy-milk is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
10. the person drinking fanta is the photographer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |     3      |       4        |
| Beverage      | almond-milk | soy-milk       | iced-tea        | fanta        |
| Job           | dressmaker   | firefighter | writer   | photographer |
| Movie-Genre   | mystery     | spy    | zombie | epic        |
| Pet           | frog         | cat  | fish       | ferret         |

