4. the accountant is on the left of the owner of the bird##1
5. the fan of house is on the right of the fan of rock##1
6. the fan of folk is on the right of the analyst##1
7. the accountant is on the right of the designer##1
8. the japanese is on the far right##1
9. the owner of the hamster is the russian##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |     2      |     3     |      4      |
| Job           | analyst   | designer  | accountant | mechanic |
| Music-Genre   | indie | folk       | rock       | house     |
| Nationality   | canadian       | russian    | malaysian     | japanese  |
| Pet           | goat     | hamster | mouse     | bird         |

