.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-5::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  lawyer, chef, dancer, librarian
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: documentary, adventure, zombie, disaster
There are 4 different nationalities: egyptian, mexican, chinese, british
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: badminton, rugby, ice-hockey, cricket
1. the person watching zombie movies is on the far left##1
2. the person who's sport is badminton is on the right of the lawyer##1
3. the person who's sport is rugby is on the far left##1
4. the mexican is on the left of the egyptian##1
5. the british is on the right of the person who's sport is cricket##1
6. the person who's sport is cricket is the chinese##1
7. the egyptian is on the left of the person watching documentary movies##1
8. the chef is on the right of the person watching adventure movies##1
9. the person watching documentary movies is on the right of the dancer##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |       3       |      4       |
| Job           | lawyer  | dancer    | chef | librarian |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie      | adventure    | documentary         | disaster    |
| Nationality   | mexican   | egyptian     | chinese          | british      |
| Sport         | rugby | badminton | cricket      | ice-hockey      |

