.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-6::.
There 4 different types of food: eggplant, garlic, lemon, watermelon
The people have 4 different jobs:  architect, analyst, photographer, teacher
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: satire, spy, drama, horror
4 different pets are kept: cat, ferret, turtle, chinchilla
 1. the person eating lemon is the person watching satire movies##1
 2. the person eating eggplant is the person watching spy movies##1
 3. the architect is the person watching satire movies##1
 4. the owner of the turtle is the person eating eggplant##1
 5. the person watching drama movies is the teacher##1
 6. the person eating lemon is on the left of the person eating garlic##1
 7. the photographer is on the left of the owner of the chinchilla##1
 8. the person watching satire movies is on the right of the person watching drama movies##1
 9. the photographer is on the far left##1
10. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person eating garlic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |     3      |     4     |
| Food          | eggplant  | watermelon | lemon     | garlic |
| Job           | photographer  | teacher      | architect | analyst    |
| Movie-Genre   | spy | drama  | satire    | horror  |
| Pet           | turtle   | chinchilla       | cat       | ferret      |

