.:: Puzzle 4x4-Level-1-7::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: water, soy-milk, lemonade, cola
The people have 4 different hobbies: gardening, video-games, filmmaking, writing
4 different pets are kept: rabbit, hamster, mouse, horse
The people use 4 different means of transport: boat, bike, subway, train
 1. the owner of the rabbit is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
 2. the person driving the train is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
 3. the person drinking lemonade is on the right of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 4. the owner of the hamster is on the left of the person who's hobby is filmmaking##1
 5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the owner of the horse##1
 6. the person who's hobby is filmmaking is on the left of the person who's hobby is writing##1
 7. the owner of the rabbit is the person driving the subway##1
 8. the person drinking water is on the far left##1
 9. the person drinking water is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
10. the person driving the boat is on the left of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1    |     2     |      3      |    4    |
| Beverage    | water | soy-milk     | lemonade    | cola |
| Hobby       | gardening | filmmaking    | writing | video-games |
| Pet         | hamster   | mouse  | horse        | rabbit    |
| Transport   | train   | bike | boat    | subway |

