6. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person driving the subway##1
7. the dressmaker is the person driving the subway##1
8. the person driving the ship is the person drinking fanta##1
9. the person driving the snowmobile is the person drinking almond-milk##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |      3      |     4      |
