7. the turkish is on the right of the person who's hobby is baking##1
8. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person drinking iced-tea##1
9. the russian is on the right of the person who's sport is snowboarding##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |       2       |    3     |      4      |
