6. the fan of hip-hop is on the left of the person eating cauliflower##1
7. the person driving the roller is on the left of the person driving the airplane##1
8. the person eating cauliflower is on the far right##1
9. the dutch is on the left of the fan of house##1

.:: Answer ::.
